snippet.title: Sentencing Phase Underway for Ex-Dallas Officer Amber Guyger
snippet.description:
Update: The routing source of the court video was changed, which caused a break in the livestream. You can watch the new stream, here: https://youtu.be/YhvB4CxSSqw

The Sentencing Phase of Amber Guyger was underway at a Texas courthouse. Guyger, a former Dallas police officer, could be facing decades in prison after being convicted of murder Tuesday in the fatal shooting of her black, unarmed neighbor who she said she believed was an intruder in her home. http://on.ktla.com/DWVZM #AmberGuyger #BothamJean
